class="vs_tabs_disc"><div class="vs_tabs"><a class="tsel" target="_self" href="https://www.bing.com/search?q=Mosque+Of+Bobo-Dioulasso%2c+Burkina+Faso&amp;bcid=RFMWYs5aL.AJW3VkBiyh49-KAUhS.....0g&amp;FORM=SBIIRP&amp;hq=1&amp;vsa=1" h="ID=SERP,5494.1"><div class="vs_tab" tsk="1"><span>Vue d’ensemble</span></div></a><a class="" target="_self" href="https://www.bing.com/search?q=Mosque+Of+Bobo-Dioulasso%2c+Burkina+Faso&amp;bcid=RFMWYs5aL.AJW3VkBiyh49-KAUhS.....0g&amp;FORM=SBIIRP&amp;hq=1&amp;vsa=2" h="ID=SERP,5495.1"><div class="vs_tab" tsk="2"><span>Correspondances visuelles</span></div></a><a class="" target="_self" href="https://www.bing.com/search?q=Mosque+Of+Bobo-Dioulasso%2c+Burkina+Faso&amp;bcid=RFMWYs5aL.AJW3VkBiyh49-KAUhS.....0g&amp;FORM=SBIIRP&amp;hq=1&amp;vsa=3" h="ID=SERP,5496.1"><div class="vs_tab" tsk="3"><span>Pages avec cette image</span></div></a><a class="" target="_self" href="https://www.bing.com/search?q=Mosque+Of+Bobo-Dioulasso%2c+Burkina+Faso&amp;bcid=RFMWYs5aL.AJW3VkBiyh49-KAUhS.....0g&amp;FORM=SBIIRP&amp;hq=1&amp;vsa=4" h="ID=SERP,5497.1"><div class="vs_tab" tsk="4"><span>Résoudre</span></div></a></div><div class="imgRetDiscContainer"><div id="imgRetDiscInfo" class="discicon" role="button" aria-label="Informations" aria-expanded="false"></div><div id="imgRetTooltip" class="discTooltip"><p>Ce résumé a été généré par l’IA à l’aide d’informations provenant de plusieurs sources en ligne. Consultez les liens des sources dans la section Basé sur les sources.<br><br>Les images que vous téléchargez peuvent être utilisées pour améliorer les services de traitement d’images de Bing.<br><a href="https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/privacy/privacystatement" target="_blank">Politique de confidentialité</a>|<a href="https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/servicesagreement/" target="_blank">Conditions d’utilisation</a></p></div></div></div></div></div><div class="vsaictnr aio_overflow"><div class="vsgenas aio_answer aio_clamped"><p data-bm="95">This photograph captures the dimly lit interior of the <strong>Grand Mosque of Bobo-Dioulasso</strong>, with its narrow passageways and traditional mud-brick walls. Built in the late 19th century, the mosque is one of the city's most important historical landmarks and a symbol of Burkina Faso's cultural heritage.</p>
</div><div class="aio_readall_footer"><acf-section-footer-redirection data-appns="SERP" data-kvalue="5726.1" data-locale="fr-FR" class="aio_readall_btn" data-is-ready=""><div class="acf-sfr__divider"></div><acf-button-standard data-appns="SERP" data-kvalue="5727.1" data-locale="fr-FR" data-shape="Rectangle" data-size="Default" data-style="Subtle" data-weight="Strong" data-inline-size="Auto" data-interaction-type="Positive" data-is-ready=""><a aria-disabled="false" aria-hidden="false" title="Lire tout" class="acf-button-standard__link" aria-label="Lire tout" href="https://www.bing.com/images/search?view=detailV2&amp;ccid=lvj3cQ9G&amp;id=EABC7AA58C20CE37B5B32BB16F4D780DE5883D20&amp;thid=OIP.lvj3cQ9GUxHqVbBCb3BVwQHaD8&amp;mediaurl=https%3a%2f%2fal3omk.com%2fwp-content%2fuploads%2f2021%2f12%2f61b8a2cbe3ac7.jpg&amp;cdnurl=https%3a%2f%2fth.bing.com%2fth%2fid%2fR.96f8f7710f465311ea55b0426f7055c1%3frik%3dID2I5Q14TW%252bxKw%26pid%3dImgRaw%26r%3d0&amp;exph=362&amp;expw=680&amp;q=Mosque+Of+Bobo-Dioulasso%2c+Burkina+Faso&amp;mode=overlay&amp;FORM=VSMAGC&amp;ck=B14D51CA13E198A2A499B00CF44ABADC&amp;idpp=serp&amp;ajaxhist=0&amp;ajaxserp=0#" h="ID=SERP,5498.1"><div class="acf-button-standard__label">Lire tout</div><acf-icon data-appns="SERP" data-kvalue="5728.1" data-locale="fr-FR" class="acf-button-standard__icon" data-size="M" data-is-ready=""><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="acf-icon__def" aria-hidden="true"><symbol id="acf-icon__ChevronRight__a49b1c19d49d9"><path fill="currentColor" d="M7.175 4a.94.94 0 0 0-.05 1.325L11.534 10l-4.407 4.675A.937.937 0 1 0 8.5 15.95l5-5.312a.937.937 0 0 0 0-1.276l-5-5.312A.94.94 0 0 0 7.176 4"></path></symbol></svg><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 20 20" class="acf-icon__icon" aria-hidden="true"><use href="#acf-icon__ChevronRight__a49b1c19d49d9"></use></svg></acf-icon></a></acf-button-standard><div class="acf-sfr__divider"></div></acf-section-footer-redirection></div><div class="b_cit_row" data-bm="98"><div class="cit_cards"><div class="cit_card_wrap" data-cit-num="1"><a class="cit_card" target="_blank" href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Grand_Mosque_of_Bobo-Dioulasso" h="ID=SERP,5729.1"><div class="cit_src"><div class="cico cit_favicon" style="width:20px;height:20px;"><img height="20" width="20" src="./mosq6_files/ODF.INhCOd4qElPoejfhZYl17A" role="presentation" loading="lazy" data-bm="96"></div><span class="cit_sitename">en.wikipedia.org</span></div><div class="cit_title">Grand Mosque of Bobo-Dioulasso - Wikipedia</div></a></div><div class="cit_card_wrap" data-cit-num="2"><a class="cit_card" target="_blank" href="https://djamanatours.com/2025/04/17/la-grande-mosquee-de-bobo_dioulasso/" h="ID=SERP,5729.1"><div class="cit_src"><span class="cit_sitename">djamanatours.com</span></div><div class="cit_title">La Grande Mosquée de Bobo Dioulasso - Djamana Tours</div></a></div></div><div class="cit_seeall_wrap"><div class="cit_seeall" role="button" tabindex="0" aria-label="Afficher tout"><div class="cit_seeall_favicons"><div class="cico cit_seeall_fav" style="width:20px;height:20px;"><img height="20" width="20" src="./mosq6_files/ODF.INhCOd4qElPoejfhZYl17A" role="presentation" loading="lazy" data-bm="97"></div></div><span class="cit_seeall_label">Afficher tout</span></div></div></div><div class="cit_hover" aria-hidden="true"><div class="cit_hover_list"><a class="cit_dtl" data-cit-num="1" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Grand_Mosque_of_Bobo-Dioulasso" h="ID=SERP,5731.1"><div class="cit_dtl_src"><div class="cico cit_dtl_favicon" style="width:20px;height:20px;"><img height="20" width="20" src="./mosq6_files/ODF.INhCOd4qElPoejfhZYl17A" role="presentation" loading="lazy" data-bm="37"></div><span class="cit_dtl_srcname">en.wikipedia.org</span></div><div class="cit_dtl_title">Grand Mosque of Bobo-Dioulasso - Wikipedia</div><div class="cit_dtl_snippet">The Grand Mosque of Bobo-Dioulasso is a mosque in Bobo-Dioulasso, Houet Province, Hauts-Bassins Region, Burkina Faso.</div><div class="cit_dtl_url">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Grand_Mosque_of_Bobo-Dioulasso</div></a><a class="cit_dtl" data-cit-num="2" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="https://djamanatours.com/2025/04/17/la-grande-mosquee-de-bobo_dioulasso/" h="ID=SERP,5731.1"><div class="cit_dtl_src"><span class="cit_dtl_srcname">djamanatours.com</span></div><div class="cit_dtl_title">La Grande Mosquée de Bobo Dioulasso - Djamana Tours</div><div class="cit_dtl_snippet">The Grande Mosquée de Bobo-Dioulasso, one of the city’s jewels, was built towards the end of the 19th century. It is one of Bobo-Dioulasso’s main historical landmarks. The name « Dioulassoba » means « the great house of the Dioula ».</div><div class="cit_dtl_url">https://djamanatours.com/2025/04/17/la-grande-mosquee-de-bobo_dioulasso/</div></a></div></div></div></div><div elementtiming="frp.WideTop" aria-hidden="true" style="pointer-events:none;margin-top:-1px;height:1px;width:1px;font-size:1px;position:absolute;top:0;right:0;" tabindex="-1"> &nbsp; </div></li><li class="b_ans" data-tag="" data-partnertag="" data-id="" h="SERP,5499.1"><style type="text/css">#copans_container .ca_top_sec+.answer_container .b_gs_top_gradient.gsqna_top_gradient+.b_genserp_container{padding-top:var(--smtc-gap-between-content-medium)}#copans_container .ca_top_sec+.answer_container .b_gs_top_gradient.gsqna_top_gradient+.b_genserp_container .gs_pre_cont{display:none}#copans_container .sc_line1 .sc_items .b_slidebar .slide{height:50px}#copans_container{padding-block-end:var(--mai-smtc-padding-card-default)}#copans_container .sc_line1{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;overflow:hidden;padding-block-start:10px;width:100%;max-width:1208px}#copans_container .ca_main{padding-block-start:var(--smtc-gap-between-content-x-large)}#copans_container .ca_main.no_padding{padding-block-start:0}#copans_container .ca_top_sec{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;padding-block-start:var(--smtc-gap-between-content-x-sma