></div></div><div class="b_imgcap_main"><div class="b_tpcn"><a class="tilk" aria-label="Wikipedia" redirecturl="" tabindex="-1" target="_blank" href="https://www.bing.com/ck/a?!&amp;&amp;p=bd9bdd2ae1974c0eff31c02087143420f432b50ba1c6e3dd690df76d5558660cJmltdHM9MTc4MDA5OTIwMA&amp;ptn=3&amp;ver=2&amp;hsh=4&amp;fclid=1c081d11-68f9-6c17-09db-0beb699d6d83&amp;psq=Mosque+Of+Bobo-Dioulasso%2c+Burkina+Faso&amp;u=a1aHR0cHM6Ly9lbi53aWtpcGVkaWEub3JnL3dpa2kvR3JhbmRfTW9zcXVlX29mX0JvYm8tRGlvdWxhc3Nv&amp;ntb=1" h="ID=SERP,5191.1"><div class="tpic"><div class="wr_fav" data-priority="2"><div class="cico siteicon" style="width:32px;height:32px;"><img src="./mosq6_files/ODF(5).INhCOd4qElPoejfhZYl17A" height="32" width="32" alt="icône du web mondial" class="rms_img" data-bm="74"></div></div></div><div class="tptxt"><div class="tptt">Wikipedia</div><div class="tpmeta"><div class="b_attribution" tabindex="-1"><cite>https://en.wikipedia.org › wiki › Gran…</cite><span id="SERP5101" class="b_tranthis">Traduire ce résultat</span></div></div></div></a></div><h2 class=""><a target="_blank" href="https://www.bing.com/ck/a?!&amp;&amp;p=bd9bdd2ae1974c0eff31c02087143420f432b50ba1c6e3dd690df76d5558660cJmltdHM9MTc4MDA5OTIwMA&amp;ptn=3&amp;ver=2&amp;hsh=4&amp;fclid=1c081d11-68f9-6c17-09db-0beb699d6d83&amp;psq=Mosque+Of+Bobo-Dioulasso%2c+Burkina+Faso&amp;u=a1aHR0cHM6Ly9lbi53aWtpcGVkaWEub3JnL3dpa2kvR3JhbmRfTW9zcXVlX29mX0JvYm8tRGlvdWxhc3Nv&amp;ntb=1" h="ID=SERP,5191.2">Grand Mosque of Bobo-Dioulasso - Wikipedia</a></h2><p class="b_lineclamp2">The Grand Mosque of Bobo-Dioulasso is a mosque in Bobo-Dioulasso, Houet Province, Hauts-Bassins Region, Burkina Faso.</p></div></div><div class="b_caption b_rich"></div></li><li class="b_algo" data-id="" iid="SERP.5761" data-bm="9"><div class="b_imgcap_altitle b_imgcap_nosc"><div class="b_imgcap_img"><div><a target="_blank" title="Explorer cette image" href="https://www.bing.com/images/search?view=detailV2&amp;ccid=LA6ZYoMf&amp;id=D880BDBA05B86A2AC199B8753F955797ED49B37D&amp;thid=OIP.LA6ZYoMfEzkAbmKGfPpPiwHaFj&amp;mediaurl=https://djamanatours.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/489927962_122228209454224223_4229349130404436860_n.jpg&amp;q=Mosque+Of+Bobo-Dioulasso%2c+Burkina+Faso&amp;ck=8E815287A12785B028A12FBA5A07BF7D&amp;idpp=rc&amp;expw=2048&amp;exph=1536&amp;form=rc2idp" h="ID=SERP,5467.1"><img src="./mosq6_files/OIP.LA6ZYoMfEzkAbmKGfPpPiwHaFj" data-priority="2" height="108" width="108" class="b_circleImage b_ci_image_overlay b_onfaimg  rms_img" fdopt="False" aria-hidden="true" data-bm="75"></a></div></div><div class="b_imgcap_main"><div class="b_tpcn"><a class="tilk" aria-label="djamanatours.com" redirecturl="" tabindex="-1" target="_blank" href="https://www.bing.com/ck/a?!&amp;&amp;p=ffc2cc6cfdc8f3dfe98836821088e4b6713197dcf05a96dc75ea5d8bc98620abJmltdHM9MTc4MDA5OTIwMA&amp;ptn=3&amp;ver=2&amp;hsh=4&amp;fclid=1c081d11-68f9-6c17-09db-0beb699d6d83&amp;psq=Mosque+Of+Bobo-Dioulasso%2c+Burkina+Faso&amp;u=a1aHR0cHM6Ly9kamFtYW5hdG91cnMuY29tLzIwMjUvMDQvMTcvbGEtZ3JhbmRlLW1vc3F1ZWUtZGUtYm9ib19kaW91bGFzc28v&amp;ntb=1" h="ID=SERP,5211.1"><div class="tpic"><div class="wr_fav" data-priority="2"><div class="cico siteicon" style="width:32px;height:32px;"><img src="./mosq6_files/ODLS.A2450BEC-5595-40BA-9F13-D9EC6AB74B9F" height="32" width="32" alt="icône du web mondial" class="rms_img" data-bm="76"></div></div></div><div class="tptxt"><div class="tptt">djamanatours.com</div><div class="tpmeta"><div class="b_attribution" tabindex="-1"><cite>https://djamanatours.com › la-grand…</cite><span id="SERP5102" class="b_tranthis">Traduire ce résultat</span></div></div></div></a></div><h2 class=""><a target="_blank" href="https://www.bing.com/ck/a?!&amp;&amp;p=ffc2cc6cfdc8f3dfe98836821088e4b6713197dcf05a96dc75ea5d8bc98620abJmltdHM9MTc4MDA5OTIwMA&amp;ptn=3&amp;ver=2&amp;hsh=4&amp;fclid=1c081d11-68f9-6c17-09db-0beb699d6d83&amp;psq=Mosque+Of+Bobo-Dioulasso%2c+Burkina+Faso&amp;u=a1aHR0cHM6Ly9kamFtYW5hdG91cnMuY29tLzIwMjUvMDQvMTcvbGEtZ3JhbmRlLW1vc3F1ZWUtZGUtYm9ib19kaW91bGFzc28v&amp;ntb=1" h="ID=SERP,5211.2">La Grande Mosquée de Bobo Dioulasso - Djamana Tours</a></h2><p class="b_lineclamp2"><span class="news_dt">17 avr. 2025</span>&nbsp;· The Grande Mosquée de Bobo-Dioulasso, one of the city’s jewels, was built towards the end of the 19th century. It is one of Bobo-Dioulasso’s main …</p></div></div><div class="b_caption b_rich"></div></li><li class="b_algo" data-id="" iid="SERP.5762" data-bm="10"><div class="b_tpcn"><a class="tilk" aria-label="wikiland.org" redirecturl="" tabindex="-1" target="_blank" href="https://www.bing.com/ck/a?!&amp;&amp;p=a7c94c8cb4cd897133c4244b84bc6a37ca40a9c32ea911845c76266561f43392JmltdHM9MTc4MDA5OTIwMA&amp;ptn=3&amp;ver=2&amp;hsh=4&amp;fclid=1c081d11-68f9-6c17-09db-0beb699d6d83&amp;psq=Mosque+Of+Bobo-Dioulasso%2c+Burkina+Faso&amp;u=a1aHR0cHM6Ly93aWtpbGFuZC5vcmcvZnIvR3JhbmRfTW9zcXVlX29mX0JvYm8tRGlvdWxhc3Nv&amp;ntb=1" h="ID=SERP,5230.1"><div class="tpic"><div class="wr_fav" data-priority="2"><div class="cico siteicon" style="width:32px;height:32px;"><img src="./mosq6_files/ODF(6).LqhB-5FuY9WoeEhnjLwURA" height="32" width="32" alt="icône du web mondial" class="rms_img" data-bm="77"></div></div></div><div class="tptxt"><div class="tptt">wikiland.org</div><div class="tpmeta"><div class="b_attribution" tabindex="-1"><cite>https://wikiland.org › fr › Grand_Mosque_of_Bobo-Dioulasso</cite></div></div></div></a></div><h2 class=""><a target="_blank" href="https://www.bing.com/ck/a?!&amp;&amp;p=a7c94c8cb4cd897133c4244b84bc6a37ca40a9c32ea911845c76266561f43392JmltdHM9MTc4MDA5OTIwMA&amp;ptn=3&amp;ver=2&amp;hsh=4&amp;fclid=1c081d11-68f9-6c17-09db-0beb699d6d83&amp;psq=Mosque+Of+Bobo-Dioulasso%2c+Burkina+Faso&amp;u=a1aHR0cHM6Ly93aWtpbGFuZC5vcmcvZnIvR3JhbmRfTW9zcXVlX29mX0JvYm8tRGlvdWxhc3Nv&amp;ntb=1" h="ID=SERP,5230.2">Grande Mosquée de Bobo-Dioulasso - wikiland.org</a></h2><div class="b_caption"><p class="b_lineclamp2">En échange, Sanou demanda au roi de Sia de faire construire une mosquée. Le royaume de Kénédougou fut stoppé à environ 30 km de la capitale, Sia, et c'est ainsi que fut construite la Grande Mosquée de …</p></div></li><li class="b_algo" data-id="" iid="SERP.5763" data-bm="11"><div class="b_tpcn"><a class="tilk" aria-label="savaneecho.fr" redirecturl="" tabindex="-1" target="_blank" href="https://www.bing.com/ck/a?!&amp;&amp;p=aa95da19092366b3ab6c0a792f37a48f336efffceb8b9ef806d7a3e7da28bd20JmltdHM9MTc4MDA5OTIwMA&amp;ptn=3&amp;ver=2&amp;hsh=4&amp;fclid=1c081d11-68f9-6c17-09db-0beb699d6d83&amp;psq=Mosque+Of+Bobo-Dioulasso%2c+Burkina+Faso&amp;u=a1aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuc2F2YW5lZWNoby5mci9hcnRpY2xlcy9ncmFuZGUtbW9zcXVlZS1ib2JvLWRpb3VsYXNzby1wYXRyaW1vaW5l&amp;ntb=1" h="ID=SERP,5249.1"><div class="tpic"><div class="wr_fav" data-priority="2"><div class="cico siteicon" style="width:32px;height:32px;"><img src="./mosq6_files/ODF(7).IJiX_hi0LsB3Fh6hsG0i4Q" height="32" width="32" alt="icône du web mondial" class="rms_img" data-bm="78"></div></div></div><div class="tptxt"><div class="tptt">savaneecho.fr</div><div class="tpmeta"><div class="b_attribution" tabindex="-1"><cite>https://www.savaneecho.fr › articles › grande-mosquee...</cite></div></div></div></a></div><h2 class=""><a target="_blank" href="https://www.bing.com/ck/a?!&amp;&amp;p=aa95da19092366b3ab6c0a792f37a48f336efffceb8b9ef806d7a3e7da28bd20JmltdHM9MTc4MDA5OTIwMA&amp;ptn=3&amp;ver=2&amp;hsh=4&amp;fclid=1c081d11-68f9-6c17-09db-0beb699d6d83&amp;psq=Mosque+Of+Bobo-Dioulasso%2c+Burkina+Faso&amp;u=a1aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuc2F2YW5lZWNoby5mci9hcnRpY2xlcy9ncmFuZGUtbW9zcXVlZS1ib2JvLWRpb3VsYXNzby1wYXRyaW1vaW5l&amp;ntb=1" h="ID=SERP,5249.2">La Grande Mosquée de Bobo-Dioulasso : un joyau de terre et de foi</a></h2><div class="b_caption"><p class="b_lineclamp2">Au cœur de Bobo-Dioulasso, deuxième ville du Burkina Faso, se dresse une architecture saisissante : la Grande Mosquée de Dioulassoba, souvent appelée “mosquée de Dioulasso-bâ”.</p></div></li><li class="b_algo" data-id="" iid="SERP.5764" data-bm="12"><div class="b_tpcn"><a class="t