zc28&amp;ntb=1" h="ID=SERP,5332.2">La Grande Mosquée de Bobo-Dioulasso : Trésor de l’architecture …</a></h2><div class="b_caption"><p class="b_lineclamp2">Érigée vers 1880 sous l’impulsion de l’Almamy Sidiki Sanou, la Grande Mosquée de Bobo-Dioulasso est un chef-d’œuvre soudano-sahélien et un symbole religieux et culturel majeur de la ville.</p></div></li><li class="b_algo" data-id="" iid="SERP.5768" data-bm="16"><div class="b_tpcn"><a class="tilk" aria-label="One Chaï" redirecturl="" tabindex="-1" target="_blank" href="https://www.bing.com/ck/a?!&amp;&amp;p=60b9bbed54ecfa3ffd583c0fc20b0d9f390106e97bb6f1aeb3fb59005040a036JmltdHM9MTc4MDA5OTIwMA&amp;ptn=3&amp;ver=2&amp;hsh=4&amp;fclid=1c081d11-68f9-6c17-09db-0beb699d6d83&amp;psq=Mosque+Of+Bobo-Dioulasso%2c+Burkina+Faso&amp;u=a1aHR0cHM6Ly9vbmVjaGFpLmZyL3Bhbm8tMzYwLW1vc3F1ZWUtZGUtYm9iby1kaW91bGFzc28v&amp;ntb=1" h="ID=SERP,5353.1"><div class="tpic"><div class="wr_fav" data-priority="2"><div class="cico siteicon" style="width:32px;height:32px;"><img src="./mosq6_files/ODF(9).rR2cgdImn7LT6H5jeeVOFw" height="32" width="32" alt="icône du web mondial" class="rms_img" data-bm="86"></div></div></div><div class="tptxt"><div class="tptt">One Chaï</div><div class="tpmeta"><div class="b_attribution" tabindex="-1"><cite>https://onechai.fr</cite></div></div></div></a></div><h2 class=""><a target="_blank" href="https://www.bing.com/ck/a?!&amp;&amp;p=60b9bbed54ecfa3ffd583c0fc20b0d9f390106e97bb6f1aeb3fb59005040a036JmltdHM9MTc4MDA5OTIwMA&amp;ptn=3&amp;ver=2&amp;hsh=4&amp;fclid=1c081d11-68f9-6c17-09db-0beb699d6d83&amp;psq=Mosque+Of+Bobo-Dioulasso%2c+Burkina+Faso&amp;u=a1aHR0cHM6Ly9vbmVjaGFpLmZyL3Bhbm8tMzYwLW1vc3F1ZWUtZGUtYm9iby1kaW91bGFzc28v&amp;ntb=1" h="ID=SERP,5353.2">La mosquée de Bobo-Dioulasso - Burkina [Panoramique 360]</a></h2><div class="b_caption"><p class="b_lineclamp2"><span class="news_dt">28 mars 2013</span>&nbsp;· Visite panoramique à 360 degrés de la plus belle mosquée de style soudanais du Burkina Faso à Bobo-Dioulasso au